title: Dolphins & Gorillas || Good Omens Puppet Animation
author: Crayfish Coffee
comment: One of my favorite parts of the book!! Man, so much to love here! All the movements Crowley made, their chairs being different, the little ribbon wine! I absolutely LOVED the different camera angles, and the focus changing was so cool! I can tell you put so much work into it, it's absolutely lovely!
I like that their talking cards have their own character flair!
i know nothing about good omens but i really enjoyed this! it's got a really good vibe.
description:
A fun little puppet animation assignment. Had a blast making little puppet Crowley and Aziraphale.

✦ SONG:
Hey Ya! (piano version) - Postmodern Jukebox
